      """
    When executing query:
      """
      MATCH (n:A) WITH n LIMIT 1
      MATCH (n)-[:REL]->(m)
      RETURN m.id AS id
      ORDER BY id
      """
    Then the result should be, in order:
      | id |
      | 1  |
    And no side effects

  Scenario: Limit before top
    And having executed:
